@startuml Sequence_ChatTutoring
title Detailed Sequence - RAG-Powered AI Tutoring

actor Student
participant "Chat UI" as UI
participant "FastAPI" as API
participant "Chat Service" as ChatSvc
participant "History Manager" as History
participant "RAG Engine" as RAG
participant "Vector DB" as Vector
participant "Groq LLM (LLaMA-3)" as Groq
participant "MongoDB" as DB

Student -> UI: "Explain SQL Joins in my path"
UI -> UI: Add user message to local state

UI -> API: POST /api/chat/stream/
API -> ChatSvc: orchestrate_response(query, history)

ChatSvc -> History: fetch_recent_history(user_id, limit=10)
History -> DB: find_chat_history
DB -> History: messages[]
History -> ChatSvc: formatted_history

ChatSvc -> RAG: search_context(query)
RAG -> RAG: embed_query(query)
RAG -> Vector: similarity_search(query_vector, top_k=3)
Vector -> RAG: relevant_document_chunks[]
RAG -> ChatSvc: context_payload

ChatSvc -> ChatSvc: Construct System Prompt\n(Identity + Context + Rules)

ChatSvc -> Groq: initiate_streaming_request(prompt)
Groq -> ChatSvc: Token Stream Start

loop For each token chunk
    ChatSvc -> API: Send SSE Event (chunk)
    API -> UI: SSE Stream (text)
    UI -> UI: Append chunk to message bubble
end

Groq -> ChatSvc: Stream Complete

ChatSvc -> DB: save_interaction(user_msg, assistant_msg)
DB -> ChatSvc: success

UI -> Student: [Full Response Displayed]

@enduml
